ease of streamflow and groundwater storage, could threaten the sustainability of surface and subsurface water resources for this critical source region of Asia's large rivers. The accumulation of TWS following the rise of surface water in north TP could increase spilling of lakes and thus risks of floods and debris flows.{$<$}/p{$>$}},
