munities include researchers and practitioners interested in common pool resource governance, adaptive management, comanagement and decentralization, citizen science, and democratic accountability, as well as those interested in applying new approaches for empirical research …  [↵][1]1To whom correspondence may be addressed. Email: pferraro\{at\}jhu.edu or arunagra\{at\}umich.edu.  [1]: \#xref-corresp-1-1},
